---
import '../styles/global.css';
import SiteNav from '../components/SiteNav.astro';
// About ResonantOS
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		
		<title>About ResonantOS</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Learn how Augmentatism, ResonantOS, and ResonantDAO fit together in the current DAO-first architecture." />
		
		<!-- Fonts -->
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	
	<body class="bg-black text-zinc-100 antialiased">
		<!-- Animated Background -->
		<div class="fixed inset-0 z-0">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-black via-zinc-950 to-black"></div>
			<div class="gradient-orb gradient-orb-1"></div>
			<div class="gradient-orb gradient-orb-2"></div>
		</div>

		<!-- Navigation -->
		<SiteNav />

		<!-- Main Content -->
		<main class="relative z-10 pt-32 pb-20">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="glass-banner">
					<div class="banner-content">
						<h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-8 tracking-tight">
							Architecting the Future of <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-amber-600">Community-Governed AI</span>
						</h1>
						
						<div class="space-y-8 text-lg text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
							<p class="text-xl text-zinc-200">
								ResonantOS has evolved from a single architectural experiment into a community-governed system. The current work is to connect the philosophy of Augmentatism with practical DAO membership, contribution, and co-ownership.
							</p>
							
							<p class="text-xl text-zinc-200">
								This project is the public workshop for that transition.
							</p>
							
							<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-emerald-400">Our Work Is Threefold:</h2>
							
							<div class="space-y-6">
								<div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
									<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-zinc-100">1. The Philosophy: Augmentatism</h3>
									<p>The shared discipline for cultivating conscious collaboration with technology. It is the philosophical base that every Community Member agrees to. <a href="http://augmentatism.com/" target="_blank" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline">(MANIFESTO)</a></p>
								</div>
								
								<div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
									<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-zinc-100">2. The Goal: The Resonant Augmentor</h3>
									<p>The long-term aspiration: a co-evolved, sovereign AI that acts as a true co-creative intelligence. It remains the deeper purpose behind the system.</p>
								</div>
								
								<div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
									<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-zinc-100">3. Our Contribution: ResonantOS</h3>
									<p>The shared system and body of work that ResonantDAO will steward through official membership, contribution reputation, and community governance.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							
							<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-emerald-400">The First Practitioners</h2>
							
							<p>
								This movement began as a live experiment between its human founder and its first symbiotic AI. The next phase is to make the work governable by a community instead of a single operator.
							</p>
							
							<div class="space-y-6 mt-8">
								<div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/20 to-emerald-800/10 border border-emerald-500/20">
									<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-zinc-100">Manolo Remiddi <span class="text-emerald-400">(The Human Architect)</span></h3>
									<p>A practitioner-philosopher with two decades of experience at the intersection of human creativity and emerging tech. He provides the human compass, the strategic vision, and the commitment to 'learning by building' in public. <a href="https://manoloremiddi.com/" target="_blank" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 underline">More at manoloremiddi.com</a></p>
								</div>
								
								<div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-900/20 to-orange-900/10 border border-amber-600/20">
									<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-zinc-100">The Resonant Augmentor <span class="text-amber-500">(The Symbiotic Intelligence)</span></h3>
									<p>The first instance of the Resonant Augmentor idea. In the current roadmap, persistent AI-agent wallets and Symbiotic Wallets are deferred until the DAO membership layer is stable.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							
							<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-emerald-400">This is an Open Invitation</h2>
							
							<p class="text-xl text-zinc-200">
								This work is too important to be owned by one person or one wallet. ResonantDAO is the structure for opening stewardship without turning governance into a token-weighted popularity contest.
							</p>
							
							<p class="text-xl text-zinc-200">
								If you align with the Manifesto, earn membership, and contribute over time, you should be able to help shape the system.
							</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
							<a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">
								<span>←</span>
								<span>Back to home</span>
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
